# count

**Instance Property**

The number of items in the series.

## Declaration

```swift
var count: Int { get }
```

## Discussion

You can access the items in the series using the corresponding query. For example, to access route data, use a [doc://com.apple.healthkit/documentation/HealthKit/HKWorkoutRouteQuery] object.
